{"tid":1964554,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【個股討論】27.HK 銀河中的老虎機","createTime":"2020-04-09T01:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T13:38:25.000Z","uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"65bd56aa4f9aaded7605e177cb15aaa9a5828fbd","tid":1964554,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"其實𠵱隻以其他人經驗嚟講好撚好玩，不過我對操作佢冇乜實際經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n稍為了解基本分析都知，澳門股都係睇 Enterprise Value (EV/EBITDA) 啫，當佢 P/E 咁玩就得<br />\n<br />\n我數都懶得計，是但攞分投行二世祖報告嘅 2021 forecast EV/EBITDA，除返佢預測出嚟嘅倍數，一倍 EV/EBITDA 大約 HK$4.8 左右<br />\n<br />\n歷史統計<br />\n低值 =&gt; 9 倍 = $43.2<br />\n中值 =&gt; 13 倍 = $62.4<br />\n高值 =&gt; 16 倍 = $72.8<br />\n<br />\n𠵱隻嘢好玩嘅地方就係近乎中長線直盤<br />\n即係近幾年嚟睇月線 MACD 一牛叉就直上到頂<br />\n跌都一樣，一熊叉就死落到底<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，如果咁睇嘅話，27 自己就係一部老虎機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果咁，我諗梗將來可唔可以用啲冇時間值嘅工具對付佢？eg. 股票期貨<br />\n<br />\n不過都係睇定啲先，個市有機會插返落 22000 補裂口先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786f6a8df52c36dae3812c3c40d6547be645d6a9","tid":1964554,"uid":202830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:07:47.000Z","msg":"今日升成4%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0b822c081886ef8d5a52c78065eb66e491d5be","tid":1964554,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"786f6a8df52c36dae3812c3c40d6547be645d6a9","tid":1964554,"uid":202830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:07:47.000Z","msg":"今日升成4%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:09:04.000Z","msg":"而家我唔會高J，睇吓有冇機會個地球上最垃圾指數死返落去"},{"pid":"b271986efc7e73bab5c07d49c0e6e6b1f3a8ec8a","tid":1964554,"uid":354348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"銀河擺明就係炒緊等疫情恢復後<br />\n復甦帶動博彩業收入/賭收"},{"pid":"f2e9fdad1ebf293b2fd9